                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(center)\">\n                <date>October 13th 1863</date>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(center)\">\n                <placeName>San Francisco California</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">My dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">I suppose<lb/> you are <sic>surprized</sic> I did not write to you\n                for<lb/> so long. I have nothing of much interest to<lb/> you. Enclosed I send you\n                some items, which<lb/> probably you may be disposed to notice in<lb/> your Journal.\n                I have only stated facts<lb/> up to the present I have not yet received<lb/> the\n                parcel you sent me it has been mislaid<lb/> but they have promised to look for it\n                and<lb/> send it to me, and then I will acknowledge<lb/> it. Your Books I find hard\n                to sell. One<lb/>\n                <sic>sett</sic> I have sold. I will collect the money<lb/> and send it to you\n                shortly as also some from<lb/> myself. I think I could sell 2 <sic>setts</sic>\n                of<lb/> your <sic>portuguese</sic>\n                <add>מחזורים</add> complete if<lb/> you have them the Octavo Edition send<lb/> me\n                the lowest price, and let the freight be<lb/> small as the people grudge to pay\n                the<lb/> same. I send you enclosed a prospectus<lb/> of my proposed little work\n                which I intend<lb/> shortly to publish and then will send some<lb/> copies to you by\n                opportunities which may often<lb/> be same expense..possibly you can dispose</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3cj8859v/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
